            <title>[LU-14537] directory migration failed with -EXDEV if parent directory and sub file have different project ID</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14537</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mdd_migrate_sanity_check() doesn&apos;t need to check project ID since it&apos;s an internal layout change, otherwise it may fail with -EXDEV if subfile project ID is different from that of parent directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
